survey_response.review_text: ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ Me 66 & my wife 64 year old, may have visited couple of dentists earlier, but never experienced the the treatment on all levels like; the most important of all  PAINLESS  TREATMENT, cleanliness,  personal attendance,  subordinates, staff, time management anywhere before.  In fact I have personally suggested Dr. Manish Sonawne to train young and new aspirant Dentists so that the fear of Dental treatment shall vanish from the mind set of Every dental patient.  ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐

Doctor Manish has an eye for detail. He understands the root cause of the problem and then devises a permanent solution for the same. Moreover his approach is consultative not like other dentists which state a one way solution.secondly he ensures that one understands the problem in detail and goes that extra mile to explain the issue in depth before operating. Thirdly he is extremely co-operative and adjusting. Lastly, due to his knowledge and experience he knows how to go about the entire procedure by ensuring there is minimum / zero pain to the client & he is always available for after service as well. All of the above demonstrate that his intention is to handhold the client to give the best possible permanent solution. I would definitely recommend him for all dental surgery / cosmetic enhancement procedures.

Due to my past experience with another Doctor I've always been scared of Dentists.  I've been avoiding my dental issues for the same reason. Dr. Manish S. Sonawane was recommended by a friend & I'm really happy & satisfied with the treatment.  Dr.  Manish is really good with his work.  My wisdom tooth extracted & stitches didn't hurt,  the treatment was painless, comfortable & within my budget. I didn't get pain even after the anesthesia effect went off. I truly recommended Dr. Manish S. Sonawane to everyone who is avoiding dental treatment because they are scare of Dentists or pain. You'll not regret getting treatment done from Dr.  Manish.

Dr. Manish is extremely credible and proficient in his practice. I experienced a great service (teeth cleaning and filling). I did not feel any discomfort or sensitivity or any sort of pain. His expertise combined with world class instruments made all the difference. The results were excellent!! My 5 year old son also was very happy with his cavity filling. Thank you Dr. Manish for your efforts and great work! We wish you all the very best!
